Package com.constantcontact.util

Interface Summary
IRestClient Interface for RestClient in Constant Contact.
 

Class Summary
Config Main Configuration structure in Constant Contact.
Config.Auth OAuth2 Authorization related configuration options.
Config.COLUMN_NAMES Collumn names in Constant Contact Activities flow.
These are used for ExportContactsRequest and AddContactsRequest requests in BulkActivitiesService.
Config.Endpoints Contains a list with all REST endpoints.
Config.Errors Errors to be returned for various exceptions in the Constant Contact flow.
Config.HTTP_CODES HTTP Return Codes in Constant Contact flow.
Config.Login Login related configuration options in Constant Contact.
These are used for the login part of the authentication flow.
CUrlRequestError A single CUrl Request Error in Constant Contact.
CUrlResponse A single CURL Response in Constant Contact.
RestClient Implementation of REST client in Constant Contact.
